going on? And so when is your next vacation? And when's that happening? And you're going to turn

00:54:08.199 --> 00:54:13.560
your phone off. You're going to take the SIM card out. I don't want you available because otherwise

00:54:13.560 --> 00:54:19.399
other people don't know to learn, to work around that absence, that planned absence,

00:54:19.399 --> 00:54:21.399
which is an incredibly important business skill to develop.

00:54:22.760 --> 00:54:27.080
I would love to add like kind of in this like financial, you know, there's a reason. I mean,

00:54:27.639 --> 00:54:33.719
I have no doubt in my mind whatsoever that the thing that has helped my career the most is

00:54:33.719 --> 00:54:39.479
investing in my own kind of personal emotional development. I think, you know, like jobs are

